  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The stocky creature within snuffles curiously at the inside of the shell.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">whimsical</span> nature, with a proclivity towards joyful play.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一颗活生生的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已可孵化！</span><br><br>卵壳内敦实的生物正好奇地发出鼻息声。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有特殊的基因潜质，具有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">异想天开</span>的性情，并倾向愉快地玩耍。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>矮胖生物在殼裡好奇地嗅聞。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">異想天開</span>性情，並傾向愉快地玩耍。"
  },
